{"word":"H7951 - שָׁלָה - shâlâh - shaw-law' - Be happy - சந்தோஷமாயிரு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שָׁלָה"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be happy / சந்தோஷமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுகித்திரு, சுகம், செல்வம்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be at rest, to prosper, to be quiet, to be at ease (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be or to have quiet"},{"paragraph":"2) to be at ease, to prosper"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> The second form being used in Job 3:26; a primitive root; to be <i>tranquil</i>, that is, <i>secure</i> or <i>successful</i>: - be happy, prosper, be in safety."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7951 - שָׁלָה - shâlâh - shaw-law'/7951\">H7951</a>, <a href=\"#/H7952 - שָׁלָה - shâlâh - shaw-law'/7952\">H7952</a>, <a href=\"#/H7956 - שֵׁלָה - Shêlâh - shay-law'/7956\">H7956</a>, <a href=\"#/H7959 - שֶׁלֶו - shelev - sheh'-lev/7959\">H7959</a>, <a href=\"#/H7961 - שָׁלֵו - shâlêv - shaw-lave'/7961\">H7961</a>, <a href=\"#/H7962 - שַׁלְוָה - shalvâh - shal-vaw'/7962\">H7962</a>, <a href=\"#/H7987 - שְׁלִי - shᵉlîy - shel-ee'/7987\">H7987</a>, <a href=\"#/H8024 - שֵׁלָנִי - Shêlânîy - shay-law-nee'/8024\">H8024</a>"}]}